Package: textcleaner
Title: A Package to Prepare and Clean Text Data for Bag of Words
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Verity", "Gribble",email = "vgrbbl@yahoo.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: The package wordClean is intended to prepare and clean data ready
                   for use for bag of words.  It removes stopwords, punctiuation
                   numbers, converts text to lowercase, and creates a word corpus
                   , vector source and term document matrix for textual data.  
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
Imports: tm
